item.description:
SoftLayer_Network_Vlan_Firewall::approveBypassRequest Approve a request from technical support to bypass the firewall.
Overview Approve a request from technical support to bypass the firewall. Once approved, support will be able to route and unroute the VLAN on the firewall.
Parameters    Name Type Description      Required Headers  authenticate SoftLayer_Network_Vlan_FirewallInitParameters  Return Values  void  Error Handling  SoftLayer_Exception_InvalidStatus   Throw the exception &ldquo;Bypass request is already approved&rdquo;

SoftLayer_Network_Vlan_Firewall::rejectBypassRequest Reject a request from technical support to bypass the firewall.
Overview Reject a request from technical support to bypass the firewall. Once rejected, IBM support will not be able to route and unroute the VLAN on the firewall.
Parameters    Name Type Description      Required Headers  authenticate SoftLayer_Network_Vlan_FirewallInitParameters  Return Values  void  Error Handling  SoftLayer_Exception_InvalidStatus   Throw the exception &ldquo;Bypass request is already rejected&rdquo;
